messages.text: R U CRAZY?!
What?
what do u want with my dad's gun?!
Just make sure he notices that it's missing.
he'll go batshit. he'll have the entire police force here.
And when he's busy tuning your home into a crime scene-
he won't notice you slipping out.
i never knew u were so devious ðŸ˜œ
It's not a sin if it's for love ðŸ˜‡
ok, loverboy - i'll tell u when the shitstorm hits...
a little bit later
cops came & they r crawling all over the place -
Great! When can you leave?
not great - my dad's so freaked out, he's giving me a curfew
What time do you have to be back home?
2 hours ago
That's so not fair!
Can you tell him you need to help a friend?
tried it - didn't work
Now what?
r u near a pay phone?
I can get to one. Why?
imagine if someone calls the cops & says they see a man downtown with the missing gun-
i can escape in the middle of the stampede
Now YOU are the devious one!
ðŸ˜ˆ
But your dad will notice you missing eventually.
eventually - but not for a while
he's calling tv stations & trying to get them to report on his stupid gun -
but they're still talking about the flood
he'll be on the phone for hours
On my way out to make the call.
You should be able to escape soon.
where do we meet?
My friend Ed's playing with his band somewhere near Coleman Place.
I'll send you the address.
a little bit later
finally out
Yeah! See you soon!!
a little bit later
hey- my GPS keeps sending me to the wrong address
text it 2 me again
I don't understand - I can't find it either.
My GPS is acting screwy. Telling me to go underground.
u don't know how to get to ur friend's band?
Never been there before. I keep going round in circles.
HOLY HELL!
what is it??!!!
A huge lightning bolt just struck a electric pole-
Now it's on fire - shooting sparks everywhere!
Aaron be careful-
AARON?!!
i'm using speech to text it fell and almost hit my car
there's lighting all over the fucking place
christ another one hit a building
i see it now
u must be close
i'm coming to u
no don't the building is on fire now
we gotta find a way out of here
let's take the beltway
no that's a wide open area we'll be easy pickings
we gotta stay on local roads and go really fast
better we both go back home
ok but this sucks
stay on speech to text I hate when we can't talk to each other
do you think there's some conspiracy against us?
what? like the universe doesn't want us to be together?
so it creates floods and lighting to stop us?
that makes no sense
but every time we plan to meet there's some catatsrophe stopping us
i have fate
fate?
I said faith - it translated as fate
faith makes all things possible
I didn't think you were religious
just because I don't go to church doesn't mean I don't believe in us
that we were meant to be together
so maybe my app is right
I also have fate
our love is our destiny
SHIT!
What happened?
cops behind me
they are stopping me
Eva be calm
EVA?!
a little bit later
that was scary
WHAT?!
I was speeding and my taillight was out so they stopped me
and then they searched the car and found my dad's gun
Why did you hide it in your car?
cause my dad would never think to look there
What did they do?!
they called my dad and told him they found me and his gun
then they escorted me home
and my dad took away my car keys
one good thing
What's that?
i got to watch the cops yell at my dad for being careless with his guns
r u home yet?
yeah - not fun.
My parents were worried - and mad as hell
they took away my car - and my license
Are we ever going to meet?
if the weather would just cooperate
did you hear about what lightning does?
Besides set fire to things?
on the news they said that it messes with GPS
something to do with electromagnetic pulses
It sure messed with us.
But we have to keep trying.
What if-?
What are you thinking?
You know what we need?
Just say it, Eva.
What we need is a good, reliable criminal accomplice.
